<div style="width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center; padding:0 12px;">

  <section style="
    max-width:1100px;
    width:100%;
    background:#ffffff;
    border-radius:16px;
    box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    padding:24px 24px 64px;
    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    margin:0 0 24px 0;
    text-align:left;
    font-family:'Roboto Mono', monospace;
  ">

    <style>
      .res-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .res-sub {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .res-label {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .res-box {
        display:inline-block;
        min-width: 220px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        border: 2px solid #000;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align:center;
        background:#ffffff;
      }
      .res-box span.unit {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-left: 4px;
      }
      .res-note {
        margin-top: 18px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
    </style>

    <h2 class="res-title">PRODUCTION RESULT</h2>

    <p class="res-sub">
      Dit is de <strong>ACTUAL PRODUCED</strong> voor deze shift, berekend op basis van:
      <br>
      <span style="font-size:12px;">
        (STOP LEVEL 710 − START LEVEL 710) + (STOP LEVEL 720 − START LEVEL 720)<br>
        + OUTBOUND BULK 710 + OUTBOUND BULK 720<br>
        + DISCHARGED BB 710 + DISCHARGED BB 720
      </span>
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top:8px;">
      <div class="res-label">RESULT:</div>
      <div class="res-box">
        <%= (typeof producedTotal !== 'undefined' ? producedTotal : 0) %>
        <span class="unit">kg</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="res-note">
      Controleer of deze waarde logisch is ten opzichte van de uitgevoerde productie en registraties
      in <strong>BULK</strong> en <strong>BB WAREHOUSING</strong>.
      <br>
      Klik op <strong>NEXT</strong> om de <strong>DOWNTIME</strong> en <strong>OEE</strong> te berekenen in de volgende stap.
    </p>

    <!-- FOOTER KNOP -->
    <div style="position:relative; height:60px; margin-top:8px;">
      <a
        href="/shifts/stop/step3"
        style="
          position:absolute;
          right:25px;
          bottom:-36px;
          display:inline-block;
          background:#fdc500;
          color:#000;
          border:none;
          border-radius:9999px;
          padding:8px 22px;
          font-weight:600;
          font-size:13px;
          letter-spacing:0.08em;
          text-transform:uppercase;
          text-decoration:none;
          box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        "
      >
        NEXT
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</div>
